        <%= image_tag "list_view_options_example.png", :alt => "List view options example" %>
        <div class="navigationalitems_codesnippit_container">
            <div class="navigationalitems_codesnippit_header">
                <h4>Create list view options that allow change of style for listing items (e.g. my memberships, my library)</h4>
